<p>in your code on line 133, you are just running .setControl, and not using your MotionMagicVoltage at all. if you check line 105 in the example, the way they do it is<br>
<code>m_fx.setControl(m_mmReq.withPosition(10).withSlot(0));</code></p>
<p>also in your code on line 134, youre setting the follower motor, and you should only have to ever set the leader motor if configured properly</p>
